job.name: Global Log Filter Usage
job.description:
Global Log Filter basic example.

Global Log Filter allows you to capture information from the whole job. This example shows how to capture env command data and use it later in the next step as [key-value](https://docs.rundeck.com/docs/manual/log-filters/key-value-data.html#key-value-data) data.

More information [here](https://docs.rundeck.com/docs/manual/log-filters/#log-filters).

execution.description: env ('Using env command we can extract a lot of keys/values :-)') [... 4 steps]
